object.script:
-- Tick function that will be executed every logic tick function onTick() Distance = math.floor(input.getNumber(1)) Bearing = math.floor(input.getNumber(2)*360) Ranging = math.floor(input.getNumber(3)) Pitch = input.getNumber(4)*16 Yaw = input.getNumber(5)*4 Zoom = input.getNumber(6) end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() -- Get the screen's width and height h = screen.getHeight()
screen.setColor(0, 0, 0) screen.drawRectF(0, 0, w, 7) screen.drawRectF(0, h-12, w, 12) screen.drawRectF(0, 0, 7, h) screen.drawRectF(w-6, 0, 6, h)
Y = (0.5*w) + (Yaw*0.5*w)*0.75
vZero = h * 0.8 if Pitch > 0 then P = vZero - (Pitch * 0.24 * h * 1) elseif Pitch < 0 then P = vZero + (Pitch * -0.4 * h * 0.1) elseif Pitch == 0 then P = vZero end
fZero = h-9 if Zoom > 0 then F = fZero - (Zoom * h * 0.725) elseif Zoom < 0.01 then F = fZero end
screen.drawLine(3, 9, 3, h-9) screen.drawLine(9, h-10 , w-8, h-10) screen.drawLine(w-3, 9, w-3, h-9) screen.drawLine(2, vZero, 5, vZero) screen.drawLine(w/2, h-11, w/2, h-8) screen.drawLine(w-2, fZero, w-5, fZero)
screen.setColor(0, 0, 0)-- Set draw color to green screen.drawRectF(0, 0, w, 7) screen.drawRectF(0, h-7, w, 7)
screen.setColor(42,46,33, 225) screen.drawRect((w/15)+10,(h/15)+10,w/1.8,h/1.8) screen.drawCircle(w/2, h/2, 2) screen.drawLine(w/2, (h/2)+4, w/2, (h/2)+10) screen.drawLine(w/2, (h/2)-4, w/2, (h/2)-10) screen.drawLine((w/2)+4, h/2, (w/2)+10, h/2) screen.drawLine((w/2)-4, h/2, (w/2)-10, h/2) screen.setColor(255, 255, 255)
screen.drawLine(3, 9, 3, h-9) screen.drawLine(9, h-10 , w-8, h-10) screen.drawLine(w-3, 9, w-3, h-9) screen.drawLine(2, vZero, 5, vZero) screen.drawLine(w/2, h-11, w/2, h-8) screen.drawLine(w-2, fZero, w-5, fZero)
screen.setColor(130, 67, 67) screen.drawLine(2, P, 5, P) screen.drawLine(Y, h-11, Y, h-8) screen.drawLine(w-2, F, w-5, F)
screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) if Bearing < 0 then screen.drawText(1, 1, "PORT") screen.drawTextBox((w/2)-7, 1, 15, 5, string.format('%03.0f',Bearing*-1), 0, 0) else screen.drawText(w-21, 1, "STBD") screen.drawTextBox((w/2)-7, 1, 15, 5, string.format('%03.0f',Bearing), 0, 0) end screen.drawTextBox((w/1.8)-8, h-6, 20, 5, string.format('%04.0f',Distance), 0, 0) screen.setColor(42,46,33, 225) screen.drawTextBox((w/2.1)-8, h-20, 20, 5, string.format('%03.00f',Ranging), 0, 0) screen.setColor(255, 255, 255) screen.drawText((h/1.67)+10, w-6, "M") screen.drawText((h/2)-19, w-6, "D") screen.drawText((h/2)-15, w-6, "I") screen.drawText((h/2)-12, w-6, "S") screen.drawText((h/2)-8, w-6, ":") end
